# Git commits and pushes (local only)

**Not shared project policy** — for this workspace’s agent sessions only. External contributors are not bound by this rule.

Project skill **`git-commits-and-push`**. Workflow, templates, and examples live there.

**Always:**

- **English only** (subject + body + PR text)
- Commit or push **only** when the user explicitly asks
- `type(scope): subject`; body with **what / why** for non-trivial changes
